# =============================================================================
# Monorepo environment — NO real secrets in git (team rule)
# =============================================================================
# Each developer copies the relevant *.env.example → .env locally.
# Never commit .env, .env.local, or production keys.
#
# Pointers:
# - Web (Prisma, BNHub): apps/web/.env.example
# - Admin: apps/admin/.env.example (if present)
# - Mobile (Expo): apps/mobile/.env.example (EXPO_PUBLIC_*)
# - Services: each service may ship services/<name>/.env.example
#
# Onboarding: docs/onboarding.md
# =============================================================================

NODE_ENV=development
